    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brazil-blue leading-tight mb-6">
      <span data-lang-content="en">Carnival, Culture & Currency: Brazil's Economic Heartbeat</span>
      <span data-lang-content="zh">狂欢节、文化与货币：巴西的经济脉搏</span>
      <span data-lang-content="pt">Carnaval, Cultura e Câmbio: O Pulso Econômico do Brasil</span>
    </h1>

    <img
      src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3293148/pexels-photo-3293148.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=400&fit=crop"
